item.title: Biomechanical indicators of adaptive decision making in children with unilateral cerebral palsy
item.description: The project will entail data processing and data analysis of behavioral and biomechanical data (collected) from experiments. The goal will be to develop a manuscript for publication at the end of the Spring semester 2021
